# Consolidate redirects to minimize redirect chains
# Order matters: most specific first

# Direct HTTP www to HTTPS non-www (single redirect instead of two)
http://www.salonta.ro/* https://salonta.ro/:splat 301!

# HTTP to HTTPS (non-www)
http://salonta.ro/* https://salonta.ro/:splat 301!

# HTTPS www to HTTPS non-www
https://www.salonta.ro/* https://salonta.ro/:splat 301!

